        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.35 - Fix Race Condition with Iframe Creation</h3>

            <h4>Bug Fix</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Create iframe via JavaScript after sessionStorage is set</li>
                <li>Fixes race condition when browser console is closed</li>
                <li>SessionStorage must be ready before SCORM player loads</li>
                <li>Ensures navigation data is available for intercepts</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Technical Details</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Moved iframe from static HTML to dynamic JavaScript creation</li>
                <li>Script sets sessionStorage, then creates iframe element</li>
                <li>Wrapped in IIFE for proper scoping</li>
                <li>iframe.allowFullscreen = true for fullscreen support</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Versions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.34: Disable direct navigation fallback</li>
                <li>v2.0.33: PostMessage reload for SmartLearning integration</li>
                <li>v2.0.32: Anti-reload-loop with separate tracking key</li>
                <li>v2.0.31: Add skipReload param to navigateToSlide</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
        </releasenotes>
